snippet.title: Critical Ops Web Open Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Critical Ops is now live on Facebook! Play it here! https://apps.facebook.com/criticalops/
Download and test the Android version here: https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.criticalforceentertainment.criticalops
Critical Ops is a fast-paced FPS that will test your reflexes and tactical skill. Experience the thrill of modern terrorist warfare as you fight a critical strike operation as a counter-terrorist or aim to cause destruction as a terrorist.
We've been working hard for the past year to make this happen, so join in and let us know what you think!
Bear in mind this is an alpha release, please help us by reporting any issues!

Stay updated on: www.CriticalStrikePortable.com or
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CriticalOpsGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CriticalForceEt
